               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <title>DIRECTIONS:</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>APPLY MEDICATION TO OILY AREAS OF THE FACE AND SHAVING BUMPS IN A VERY THIN LAYER. LEAVE ON OVERNIGHT. FREQUENCY OF APPLICATION: DETERMINED BY DR. THROWER.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph/>
               </text>
